  "title": "*New* Clinic / Dental Assistant (Office Hours, 5 Days, No Experience Required – Training Provided) #HJG",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist with patient registration and appointment scheduling</p></li><li><p>Maintain and update patient records and medical documentation</p></li><li><p>Support daily clinic operations, including managing supplies and inventory</p></li><li><p>Prepare consultation rooms and equipment for patient visits</p></li><li><p>Assist medical staff with basic administrative tasks</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min GCE N/O or ‘A’ Levels / Diploma and above</p></li><li><p>Keen interest in the healthcare/medical industry</p></li><li><p>No experience needed, full training will be provided</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office</p></li><li><p>Able to start work immediately</p></li></ul><p><strong>Footer</strong><br />If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> and <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> (Attn: Clinic / Dental Assistant)<br />Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p>",
